room_title: Escape room "Blood Thirst" by Epic Escape Game in Phoenix
room_description: You are a part of an elite team of Vampire Hunters in Transylvania. Your team finally located the lair of the oldest vampire known to man, Dracula. Upon entering the lair, the door behind you locks and you find yourself a part of a deadly game. You have one hour to use all your skills and wits to defeat darkness himself.
